
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>For Nivetha ❤️</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
}

body{
    min-height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff9a9e,#fad0c4);
    padding:20px;
}

.container{
    width:100%;
    max-width:800px;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
    border-radius:25px;
    padding:40px;
    color:white;
    box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    text-align:center;
}

h1{
    font-size:2.5rem;
    margin-bottom:25px;
}

.message{
    font-size:1.1rem;
    line-height:1.9;
    text-align:left;
}

.message p{
    margin-bottom:18px;
}

.heart{
    font-size:3rem;
    margin-top:20px;
    animation:heartbeat 1.5s infinite;
}

@keyframes heartbeat{
    0%,100%{
        transform:scale(1);
    }
    50%{
        transform:scale(1.2);
    }
}

@media(max-width:768px){
    .container{
        padding:25px;
    }

    h1{
        font-size:2rem;
    }

    .message{
        font-size:1rem;
        line-height:1.8;
    }
}

@media(max-width:480px){
    h1{
        font-size:1.7rem;
    }

    .message{
        font-size:0.95rem;
    }

    .heart{
        font-size:2.5rem;
    }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>Dear Nivetha ❤️</h1>

    <div class="message">
        <p>
            I never knew how much you mean to me when we first started talking.
            Until today, I still love you as much as I did since the very first day we met.
        </p>

        <p>
            Ever since you came into my life, I felt like I was the happiest.
            I just want to let you know how much you mean to me and how much I appreciate you.
        </p>

        <p>
            You never failed to make me smile.
            Things aren't getting better ever since we fought. I just miss you so much.
            Having random breakdowns, with you on my mind, wondering if you're doing fine.
        </p>

        <p>
            I'm sorry I wasn't what you wanted.
            I'm sorry I wasn't the best.
            I'm sorry I couldn't be good enough for you.
        </p>

        <p>
            I just hope everything will be okay soon.
            I really miss how we used to talk. 🥹
        </p>
        <p>
            Nee illana enala epdi iruka mudiyum nu kuda enaku theriyala.

Nee illama naan epdi irupen nu ninaichale aluga varudhu. Daily un nyabagam than varudhu. Un kooda pesuna moments, namma sirichadhu, namma pesina conversations ellam en mind la odite iruku.

Please ennai vittu poiradha.

Unna enaku romba pudikum. En friendship un mela romba pure-ah iruku. Adhanala than eppovume unna thediye varen. Un kitta pesanum, un voice kekanum, nee nalla irukiya nu therinjikanum nu thonum.

Nee pesama irukumbodhu romba valikudhu. Adha words la explain panna mudiyala. Oru empty feeling madhiri iruku.

Naan perfect illa nu enaku theriyum. Naan mistakes pannirukalam. Aana un friendship-ah naan unmaiyave cherish pannuren.

Ippo kuda enaku venum nu na, namma munnadi maari pesanum, sirikanum, normal-ah irukanum avlodhan.

Please pesu... Romba miss panren. 🥹❤️
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="heart">❤️</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
